---
/* Componente de Mantenimiento Profesional - Burbano & Bahos */
---
<div class="maintenance-wrapper">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content">
      <h1 class="brand-name">BURBANO & BAHOS</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">FIRMA LEGAL</p>
      
      <div class="divider"></div>
      
      <h2 class="status">Sitio web en construcción</h2>
      <p class="message">
        Estamos preparando nuestra presencia digital para servirle mejor.<br>
        Nuestra oficina virtual estará disponible próximamente.
      </p>

      <a href="mailto:contacto@burbanoybahos.com" class="contact-btn">
        Contactar por Correo
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .maintenance-wrapper {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    background-color: #1F4037; /* Tu verde corporativo */
    color: #e2e8f0;
    height: 100vh;
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    z-index: 9999;
  }

  .container {
    padding: 2rem;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .brand-name {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin: 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #d4af37, transparent);
    margin: 2rem auto;
    width: 60%;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .status {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .message {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #94a3b8;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .contact-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 14px 35px;
    border: 1px solid #d4af37; /* Borde dorado */
    color: #d4af37;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .contact-btn:hover {
    background-color: #d4af37;
    color: #1F4037;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
